description: Removes the specified tag or tags from the specified CloudHSM cluster. Cross-account use: No. You cannot perform this operation on an CloudHSM resource in a different Amazon Web Services account.

parameters.name: ResourceId
parameters.description: The cluster identifier (ID) for the cluster whose tags you are removing. To find the cluster ID, use  DescribeClusters.

parameters.name: TagKeyList
parameters.description: A list of one or more tag keys for the tags that you are removing. Specify only the tag keys, not the tag values. (string) ---
